1. *Podu* je sneg pokrio celu ulicu. (The snow covered the entire street.)
2. Ona je *podu* izbeljivala. (She was whitewashing the floor.)
3. On je svoje stvari razbacao po *podu*. (He scattered his things on the floor.)
4. Ona je *podu* u dnevnoj sobi istresla. (She swept the floor in the living room.)
5. *Podu* u hodniku je trebalo da se ispere. (The floor in the hallway needed to be washed.)